Adjacent to the sparkling pool is a fully equipped pool house with a kitchenette, washer/dryer, an additional bedroom if desired and full bath.The generous first-floor primary suite is a true retreat with fireplace, walk-in closet with built-ins, steam shower, heated floors and dual sinks. An additional junior en-suite on the first floor as well. Two additional bedrooms and a full bath round out the second level. Easy commute access to Silicon Valley companies, Zanotto's, shopping, O'Connor hospital and restaurants.

This charming two-story home is located on one of the best streets in the Rose Garden, just blocks from the Rose Garden park, library, Zanotto's, Bill's, Starbucks and the local public/private schools. The kitchen was remodeled in 2018/2019 with new kitchen cabinets, Carrara marble counters, Bertazzoni stainless gas range/hood, dishwasher and Liebherr refrigerator. The dining area is located between the kitchen and living room. On the second floor, there are two spacious bedrooms (each with a walk-in closet and attic storage closet), a full bathroom (separate shower stall/separate bathtub) and office area. On the first floor, there is a bedroom, half-bathroom and laundry area. The bathrooms were remodeled in 2018/2019. Hardwood floors throughout. Basement with furnace/water heater. Finished detached garage. New front/back lawns. AC.
